title: Pro-vaccination sign goes viral
description:
A pro-vaccination message from Northern NSW Intensive Care specialist Dr Rachel Heap has gone viral after a poster using the words was seen in a Colorado doctor's office and a photo shared on Facebook.
Vaccinating prevents diseases that can be fatal or have life-long consequences. For more information visit Northern Rivers Vaccination Supporters
https://nrvs.info/
